phase2.explanation:
You forgot to set the CellValueFactory AND the items!

FIX: 
1. Set cell value factory:
col.setCellValueFactory(new PropertyValueFactory<>("name"));

2. Set items:
ObservableList<Person> people = FXCollections.observableArrayList(...);
table.setItems(people);

Without CellValueFactory, the column doesn't know which property to display.

Without items, there's no data to show.

